data.description: Come see this beautifully updated split-level home in charming Mount Prospect. This 3-bedroom, 2.5-bath gem features a newly renovated kitchen with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and a stylish backsplash (3 months old). The entire home boasts fresh paint in elegant 'Magnolia Farms' gray tones, creating an inviting interior, baths updated 2017, with beautiful double shower..  Upper & main levels have hardwood floors.
